<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يَسْعى بَيْنَ أَيْدِيهِمْ وَبِأَيْمانِهِمْ يَقُولُونَ رَبَّنا أَتْمِمْ لَنا نُورَنا وَاغْفِرْ لَنا إِنَّكَ عَلى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ <span class="c2">(٨)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١١٠- وَضَرَبَ اللَّهُ مَثَلًا لِلَّذِينَ آمَنُوا امْرَأَتَ فِرْعَوْنَ إِذْ قالَتْ رَبِّ ابْنِ لِي عِنْدَكَ بَيْتاً فِي الْجَنَّةِ وَنَجِّنِي مِنْ فِرْعَوْنَ وَعَمَلِهِ وَنَجِّنِي مِنَ الْقَوْمِ الظَّالِمِينَ <span class="c2">(١١)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١١١- رَبِّ اغْفِرْ لِي وَلِوالِدَيَّ وَلِمَنْ دَخَلَ بَيْتِيَ مُؤْمِناً وَلِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ وَالْمُؤْمِناتِ وَلا تَزِدِ الظَّالِمِينَ إِلَّا تَباراً <span class="c2">(٢٨)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١١٢- قُلْ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ الْفَلَقِ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مِنْ شَرِّ ما خَلَقَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَمِنْ شَرِّ غاسِقٍ إِذا وَقَبَ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَمِنْ شَرِّ النَّفَّاثاتِ فِي الْعُقَدِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَمِنْ شَرِّ حاسِدٍ إِذا حَسَدَ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١١٣- قُلْ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ النَّاسِ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مَلِكِ النَّاسِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إِلهِ النَّاسِ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مِنْ شَرِّ الْوَسْواسِ الْخَنَّاسِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>الَّذِي يُوَسْوِسُ فِي صُدُورِ النَّاسِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مِنَ الْجِنَّةِ وَالنَّاسِ <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
